CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 25, 1961, pg. B5 reads: "Among the more than 300 guests attending the smart Chi Delta Mu Fraternity supper dance, last Saturday evening at the Pittsburgh Hilton..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five men, and five women, including one wearing dark sequined dress with matching jacket, seated at banquet table in Hilton Hotel for Chi Delta Mu supper dance
